OL,3,CConvicted teacher allowed to continue
OL,4,Cafter holding pupil upside down
OL,6,FA Cumbrian teacher convicted of
OL,7,Fassault has been allowed to continue
OL,8,Fteaching after holding a pupil upside
OL,9,Fdown by the ankles to "cheer her up".
OL,11,FMusic teacher Sean Haythornthwaite -
OL,12,Fdescribed as "quiet and calm" -
OL,13,Fclaimed he tried to take a "parental
OL,14,Frole" to make the girl laugh after she
OL,15,Fhad been hiding under a table
OL,16,Ffollowing an argument.
OL,18,FHaythornthwaite taught at Seascale
OL,19,FPrimary School, Whitehaven, at the
OL,20,Ftime of the incident in February 2022.
