OL,3,CConvicted teacher allowed to continue
OL,4,Cafter holding pupil upside down
OL,6,FHe was convicted of assault by
OL,7,Fbeating, and sentenced to 150 hours of
OL,8,Funpaid work while also ordered to pay
OL,9,F#100 in compensation at Workington's
OL,10,FWest Cumbria Magistrates' Court in
OL,11,FJuly 2022.
OL,13,FThe teacher told the school the girl
OL,14,Fwas ""laughing when he picked her up
OL,15,Fand the others in the class laughed
OL,16,Fwith her, not at her".
OL,18,FHe was reported to the police and
OL,19,Ffound guilty of assault following a
OL,20,Ftrial after a parent complained.
