OL,3,CConvicted teacher allowed to continue
OL,4,Cafter holding pupil upside down
OL,6,FMr Haythornthwaite said he made a
OL,7,F"well intended but poor choice" that
OL,8,F"ruined his my life and destroyed my
OL,9,Fteaching career".
OL,11,FHe was employed by Cumbria County
OL,12,FCouncil as a music teacher, the
OL,13,FTeaching Regulation Agency panel heard.
OL,15,FThe teacher had been working for six
OL,16,Fyears at the time of the incident and
OL,17,Fwas studying for a postgraduate
OL,18,Fcertificate in education.
