OL,3,CConvicted teacher allowed to continue
OL,4,Cafter holding pupil upside down
OL,6,FAn unnamed woman said she was "utterly
OL,7,Fshocked" when she heard about the
OL,8,Fallegation. She added it was "very
OL,9,Fmuch out of character".
OL,11,FAnother witness said the teacher was
OL,12,F"upset" and "really distressed... He
OL,13,Fwas a bit devastated... He just seemed
OL,14,Fbroken".
OL,16,FHaythornthwaite told the panel: "I
OL,17,Ftook a parental role in a situation to
OL,18,Ftry and cheer a child up because they
OL,19,Fare my responsibility and because I
OL,20,Fdid not have the knowledge to keep
OL,21,Fmyself safe in a teaching environment.
