OL,3,CConvicted teacher allowed to continue
OL,4,Cafter holding pupil upside down
OL,6,F"I made a well-intended but poor
OL,7,Fchoice, one that ruined my life and
OL,8,Fdestroyed my teaching career."
OL,10,FMr Haythornthwaite added that his
OL,11,F"only prior experience to this role
OL,12,Fhas been training adults in either
OL,13,Fadmin or retail posts".
OL,15,F"I did not have a teaching
OL,16,Fqualification and no prior experience
OL,17,Fof working in a school environment or
OL,18,Fworking with children."
